title: Curse of the Double Digits
description: "Woo hoo! It's my birthday."Becky is sure turning ten on the 10th day of the tenth month will be magical.The whole class is invited to her party, including Chad, the cutest boy in the fifth grade. So is Darlenie-the-Meanie.Becky wants to look cute for her party, but all her plans go wrong. Really wrong. The magic of turning ten disappears before she even has a chance to blow out her birthday candles. Things get so bad, she refuses to go to her own party.Becky wonders if the Curse of the Double Digits will jinx her forever.
author: Lynn Kelley
